00:10:01.980 --> 00:10:04.640
This place can carry a brighter beat

00:10:04.880 --> 00:10:07.000
Not loud, but still complete

00:10:07.060 --> 00:10:09.240
A clean card, a tiny fold

00:10:09.300 --> 00:10:11.960
A soft feeling that never gets old

00:10:12.020 --> 00:10:16.220
Price tag on the window glass

00:10:16.280 --> 00:10:20.380
One small catch of orange light

00:10:20.700 --> 00:10:25.660
Turns a practical line into a pause

00:10:25.720 --> 00:10:30.920
