be gentle and fine

00:11:02.260 --> 00:11:05.860
A reflected smile,
a pause at the edge

00:11:05.920 --> 00:11:10.260
A little light where care can be said

00:11:10.320 --> 00:11:14.280
Price tag on the window glass

