00:13:36.040 --> 00:13:40.040
Loyalty card at the counter

00:13:40.700 --> 00:13:45.460
The light goes green,
then soft and slow

00:13:46.120 --> 00:13:52.340
A gentle turn in the afternoon

00:13:53.340 --> 00:13:57.300
Where steady feelings keep their glow

00:13:58.780 --> 00:14:04.720
Counter light fades,
cloth light remains

00:14:05.580 --> 00:14:09.360
A warm beat, a tender refrain

00:14:15.680 --> 00:14:18.140
Beep, then hush

00:14:18.200 --> 00:14:22.840
Door glass glows into dusk

00:14:23.360 --> 00:14:27.640
One quick light for a borrowed code

00:14:28.260 --> 00:14:32.400
A tiny flash on the shelf-side road

00:14:32.460 --> 00:14:36.340
